  /-- The left unitor: `ùüò_ C ‚äï‚Çí X ‚âÉ X` -/
  leftAddUnitor : ‚àÄ X : C, addObj addUnit X ‚âÖ X
  /-- The right unitor: `X ‚äï‚Çí ùüò_ C ‚âÉ X` -/
  rightAddUnitor : ‚àÄ X : C, addObj X addUnit ‚âÖ X

